Imate pojma zašto ste to govorili?

00:13:40.528 --> 00:13:41.737
Ne.

00:13:41.779 --> 00:13:43.489
Zašto je netko pucao u vas?

00:13:43.531 --> 00:13:47.243
Ponavljaš mi ta pitanja, ženo,
ali ja neću znati odgovore!

00:13:47.285 --> 00:13:49.285
Ime mi je Sienna.

00:13:51.331 --> 00:13:53.331
O, Bože. Žao mi je.

00:13:55.668 --> 00:13:57.668
Zdravo.

00:13:58.129 --> 00:13:59.464
Bok.

00:13:59.506 --> 00:14:01.573
Samo, postavljaš mnogo pitanja.

00:14:01.633 --> 00:14:03.926
Da, osjećam se malo ranjivo.

00:14:04.093 --> 00:14:06.803
S nekim sam na koga ljudi pucaju.

00:14:06.971 --> 00:14:08.971
Žao mi je.

