Pitanja su važna. Pomoći
će da se oporavite.

00:14:15.271 --> 00:14:19.274
Mogu zamoliti šalicu...

00:14:25.281 --> 00:14:28.116
Smeđe je i vruće...

00:14:28.284 --> 00:14:31.537
Ljudi to piju svako jutro za energiju.

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:34.331
Čaj. -Čaj. Ne! Ono drugo.

00:14:34.499 --> 00:14:36.499
Kava. -Kava!

00:14:36.543 --> 00:14:38.585
Mogu dobiti šalicu kave?

00:14:39.879 --> 00:14:41.879
Svakako.

00:14:41.923 --> 00:14:43.923
Hvala.

00:14:49.013 --> 00:14:51.013
Veoma si organizirana.

00:14:51.599 --> 00:14:53.684
Volim kad je uredno.

00:14:54.852 --> 00:15:00.107
Hvala na pomoći u
bolnici. To je bilo hrabro.

00:15:00.275 --> 00:15:02.275
Bili su samo refleksi.

00:15:03.736 --> 00:15:05.736
Veoma žao.

00:15:09.450 --> 00:15:11.450
Veoma...

00:15:15.540 --> 00:15:17.540
Žao.

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:30.720
Imam vizije.

00:15:30.805 --> 00:15:32.806
To je od ozljede glave.

00:15:33.349 --> 00:15:36.616
Neko vrijeme nećete moći
vjerovati svojim mislima.

00:15:37.812 --> 00:15:40.522
Vidio sam masku kuge.

00:15:40.690 --> 00:15:45.027
Kakvu su liječnici nosili
u doba epidemije Crne smrti.

00:15:45.194 --> 00:15:47.194
Rekli ste nešto o tome.

00:15:47.488 --> 00:15:50.866
Govorili ste u taksiju.
Bilo je nekoherentno.

00:15:51.492 --> 00:15:53.577
Ali čula sam riječ maska.

00:15:54.162 --> 00:15:56.162
Još što?

00:15:56.289 --> 00:15:58.040
Tijela.

00:15:58.082 --> 00:16:00.125
I krv i vatra...

00:16:01.127 --> 00:16:03.127
<i>I pakao.</i>

00:16:04.714 --> 00:16:06.714
I postoji žena.

00:16:09.218 --> 00:16:11.595
Da, žena, i doimala se...

00:16:11.763 --> 00:16:13.598
<i>Traži i nađi.</i>

00:16:13.640 --> 00:16:16.350
Sve se doimalo tako opasno.

00:16:16.517 --> 00:16:18.810
Imate nekoga koga možemo nazvati.

00:16:20.104 --> 00:16:21.606
Imam?

00:16:21.648 --> 00:16:23.648
Zašto?

00:16:26.861 --> 00:16:30.322
Imao sam sat kad su
me donijeli u bolnicu?

00:16:30.490 --> 00:16:32.490
Ne.

00:16:37.538 --> 00:16:39.665
Niste nosili sat.

00:16:39.832 --> 00:16:41.334
Jako mi je važan.

00:16:41.376 --> 00:16:43.294
Bio je dar mojih roditelja.

00:16:43.336 --> 00:16:45.336
Trebate se urediti i oprati.

00:16:46.547 --> 00:16:50.133
Odjeća vam je krvava, ali
mislim da imam nešto za vas.

00:16:50.593 --> 00:16:53.804
Kad se odjenete, zvat ćemo policiju.

00:16:53.971 --> 00:16:55.556
Ne, ne.

00:16:55.598 --> 00:16:57.598
Konzulat.

00:16:57.892 --> 00:16:59.518
U redu.

00:16:59.560 --> 00:17:01.560
Konzulat.

00:17:07.777 --> 00:17:09.777
Kava.

00:17:24.085 --> 00:17:26.085
Gost korisnik

00:17:28.464 --> 00:17:30.966
Čudo od djeteta ide na studij

00:17:49.902 --> 00:17:52.279
Ignazio Busoni 
MOLIM SE DA SI DOBRO.

00:17:52.447 --> 00:17:54.447
Ignazio?

