Raj dvadeset i pet.

00:18:26.689 --> 00:18:28.689
Ignazio?

00:18:46.334 --> 00:18:48.502
Vaše stvari su u kupaonici.

00:18:49.128 --> 00:18:51.046
Isprobajte ovo.

00:18:51.088 --> 00:18:53.088
Čije je?

